  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n                        \u003cp\u003eIn the vibrant center of Forlì, Italy, within the prestigious Palazzo Calboli dall’Aste, a penthouse renovation by \u003ca href=\"https://tissellistudio.com/en/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003etissellistudioarchitetti\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e has intersected the past with modernity. Dubbed \u003ca href=\"https://tissellistudio.com/en/projects/nap/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNAP\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, this project transforms a 2,152-square-foot space into a residence where bold design choices live happily with historical preservation.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567911\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567911\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-2-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern living room with a minimalist design. Features include a large, angled mirrored wall, two contemporary sofas, a round coffee table, and exposed beams. Natural light illuminates the space.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-2-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-2-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-2-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-2-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-2.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp