exposed beams. A blurred figure is walking up the stairs.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-4-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-4-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-4-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-4-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-4.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567914\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567914\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-5-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern interior with a staircase featuring a glass and metal railing, natural wood flooring, and a small window partially obscured by the structure.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-5-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-5-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-5-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-5-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-5.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567915\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567915\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-6-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern interior with a white staircase, exposed wooden beams, a couch with cushions, and a minimalistic decor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-6-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-6-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-6-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-6-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-6.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"\u003eThe living area’s warm wooden floors and crisp white walls set the stage for custom-designed furnishings that blend simplicity with sophistication. Descending a few steps leads to the dining room, where reflective elements and colorful accents add a contemporary edge without compromising the space’s understated elegance. Here, a brushed stainless steel kitchen peninsula interacts seamlessly with a matte lacquered wood panel, which cleverly conceals the kitchen’s functional elements, maintaining a clean and unified look.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567916\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567916\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-7-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with a stainless steel island, wooden floor, pendant light, and exposed beams. Minimalist design with white walls and ceiling.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-7-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-7-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-7-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-7-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-7.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567917\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567917\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-8-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist kitchen with a stainless steel island and faucet, white panel cabinets, light wood countertop, and exposed wooden ceiling beams.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-8-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-8-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-8-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-8.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567918\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567918\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-9-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist kitchen with a metallic faucet and sink set against sleek white panel walls.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-9-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-9-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-9-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"\u003eThroughout the penthouse, materials and finishes are meticulously chosen to echo the dual narrative of history and modernity. The wooden flooring and white surfaces serve as a unifying thread, offering a neutral canvas that accentuates the vibrant mirrored details and bespoke furniture. These design choices ensure that each space flows into the next, creating a cohesive yet dynamic living environment.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567919\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567919\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-10-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist kitchen with a sleek metal countertop featuring a modern faucet, a built-in sink, and an induction cooktop, set against a backdrop of vertical panel wall design.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-10-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-10-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-10-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567920\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567920\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-11-810x456.jpg\" alt=\"Modern hallway with brown reflective panel doors, framed abstract paintings, and light wood flooring.\" width=\"810\" height=\"456\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-11-810x456.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-11-800x450.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-11-768x432.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-11-600x337.jpg 600w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567921\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567921\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-12-810x1220.jpg\" alt=\"A minimalist bathroom features a rectangular yellow sink with a sleek wall-mounted faucet, a large mirror, and concealed lighting on a white wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1220\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-12-810x1220.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-12-800x1205.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-12-768x1157.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-12-1020x1536.jpg 1020w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567923\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567923\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-13-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Bedroom with slanted wooden beams and a skylight, mirrored closet doors reflect a single bed with white bedding on wooden flooring, and a blurred figure is visible in the reflection.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-13-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-13-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-13-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-13-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-13.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"\u003eThe private quarters of the penthouse offer equally thoughtful design. The primary bedroom is distinguished by a large window overlooking the adjoining bathroom, fostering a sense of openness and continuity. Skylights bathe the room in natural light, enhancing its serene ambiance. The adjoining bathroom features bold red and mirrored surfaces, transforming a typically utilitarian space into an area of refined aesthetics. Exposed beams in this section further elevate the room, highlighting the perfect balance between functionality and design.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567924\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567924\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-14-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bathroom with two circular, backlit mirrors on white walls, a large glass-enclosed shower, and a wooden stool on the floor. Exposed beams and a slanted ceiling add character.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-14-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-14-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-14-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-14-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567925\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567925\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-15-810x1096.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bathroom with a round backlit mirror, a glass shower enclosure with a rainfall showerhead, and exposed beam ceiling. White walls and wooden accents are present.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1096\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-15-810x1096.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-15-800x1083.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-15-768x1039.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-15-1135x1536.jpg 1135w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567926\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567926\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-16-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist bathroom featuring an illuminated round mirror, a white countertop with an integrated sink, and a sleek black wall-mounted faucet and hand shower.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-16-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-16-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-16-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-16-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567927\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567927\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-17-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist bathroom with a backlit circular mirror above a white rectangular sink. A modern black shower fixture is on the adjacent wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-17-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-17-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-17-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-17-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"\u003eThis ambitious project was not without its challenges. Situated within a property protected by the Superintendency of Archaeology, Fine Arts, and Landscape, the design team had to navigate strict regulations while introducing innovative elements. The result is a residence that respects its historical context while boldly embracing contemporary design language.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567928\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567928\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-18-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom with red walls, a round mirror above a white floating sink, and a walk-in shower with a rain showerhead and glass partition.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-18-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-18-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-18-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-18-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-18.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"\u003eTissellistudioarchitetti, led by architects Filippo Tisselli and Cinzia Mondello, has a long-standing reputation for crafting spaces that merge functionality with artistic expression. Architect Marcin Dworzynski joined the fold in 2011 and adds further depth to the studio’s expertise. With roots in the local region, the firm is known for integrating international architectural trends into its projects, as exemplified by the NAP penthouse. This latest endeavor reflects their commitment to pushing boundaries while honoring tradition, offering a living experience that is as unique as it is engaging.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567929\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567929\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-19-810x1220.jpg\" alt=\"A red minimalist bathroom with two wall-mounted toilets and a large mirrored wall, reflecting the interior design.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1220\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-19-810x1220.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-19-800x1205.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-19-768x1157.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-19-1020x1536.jpg 1020w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHave you ever seen a red toilet?!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567930\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567930\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-20-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A room with red walls, a closed door, and a narrow rectangular wall fixture. A ceiling light illuminates the scene.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-20-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-20-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-20-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-20-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-20.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567931\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567931\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-21-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Abstract image featuring overlapping red geometric shapes with sharp lines and shadows.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-21-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-21-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-21-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-21-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-21.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"attachment_567932\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567932\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567932\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-22-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Three people standing behind a white wall, looking at the camera. The background is a softly lit, minimalist interior.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-22-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-22-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-22-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/NAP-Penthouse-Italy-tissellistudioarchitetti-22.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eMarcin Dworzyński, Cinzia Mondello, and Filippo Tisselli of Tissellistudioarchitetti\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFor more on the NAP Penthouse and tissellistudioarchitetti, visit \u003ca href=\"https://tissellistudio.com/en/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003etissellistudio.com\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mdworzynski/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eMarcin Dworzyński\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                        \n                                                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson-100x100.jpg\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson.jpg 2x\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"\"/\u003e                                    \u003c/p\u003e\n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eCaroline Williamson is Editor-in-Chief of Design Milk. She has a BFA in photography from SCAD and can usually be found searching for vintage wares, doing New York Times crossword puzzles in pen, or reworking playlists on Spotify.\u003c/p\u003e\n                                    \n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n                            \u003c/div\u003e\n                                            \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
